@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class
!define DATABASE entity

RECTANGLE UserInterface <<Webhook Management UI>> {
    :+ Create Webhook
    :+ Update Webhook
    :+ Delete Webhook
}

RECTANGLE WebhookService {
    :+ validateRequest()
    :+ saveWebhookData()
    :+ triggerWorkflow()
}

RECTANGLE WorkflowEngine <<Workers>> {
    :+ executeWorkflow()
}

DATABASE Supabase <<Database>> {
    :Postgres
    :Realtime
    :Storage
}

UserInterface --> WebhookService : Uses
WebhookService --> Supabase : Reads/Writes
WebhookService --> WorkflowEngine : Triggers
WorkflowEngine --> Supabase : Updates State

note right of WebhookService : Core Webhook\nConfiguration Logic
note right of WorkflowEngine : Handles Workflow\nExecution Logic

@enduml